    {
      "id": "186fea81_3e682cbc",
      "file_path": "src/main/java/org/onap/dcaegen2/services/pmmapper/App.java",
      "patchset_number": 46,
      "line": 145,
      "message": "Given this is attempting to publish VES events, you shouldnt integrate the VES publishing into the KPI Computation unit itself, you should have that as a separate action on this stream.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 4023,
        "name": "Joseph O'Leary",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "joseph.o.leary@est.tech",
        "username": "JoeOLeary"
      },
      "updated": "2020-09-15 09:23:47.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "id": "c0f14147_9c05a243",
      "file_path": "src/main/java/org/onap/dcaegen2/services/pmmapper/kpi/computation/KpiComputation.java",
      "patchset_number": 46,
      "line": 67,
      "message": "Try to keep your methods doing one thing where possible, methods with an \"and\" in their signature are generally a smell for bad design",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 4023,
        "name": "Joseph O'Leary",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "joseph.o.leary@est.tech",
        "username": "JoeOLeary"
      },
      "updated": "2020-09-15 09:23:47.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "id": "877275ce_488b5986",
      "file_path": "src/main/java/org/onap/dcaegen2/services/pmmapper/kpi/computation/KpiComputation.java",
      "patchset_number": 46,
      "line": 176,
      "message": "Can you look at the command pattern for this piece of code\nhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Command_pattern\n\nIt would improve the design a significantly.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 4023,
        "name": "Joseph O'Leary",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "joseph.o.leary@est.tech",
        "username": "JoeOLeary"
      },
      "updated": "2020-09-15 09:23:47.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "id": "9584c3c2_c0a24ad4",
      "file_path": "src/main/java/org/onap/dcaegen2/services/pmmapper/kpi/computation/KpiPublisher.java",
      "patchset_number": 46,
      "line": 1,
      "message": "I dont think you need another Publisher for this, just have the KPI computation unit return everything it needs to be published and do the publishing in a separate action on the stream in the App class reusing the existing VES publisher.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 4023,
        "name": "Joseph O'Leary",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "joseph.o.leary@est.tech",
        "username": "JoeOLeary"
      },
      "updated": "2020-09-15 09:23:47.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": true
    },
