      "file_path": "src/main/java/org/onap/dcaegen2/services/pmmapper/App.java",
      "patchset_number": 52,
      "line": 131,
      "message": "Rather than handing in the publisher as a dependency, can we align with the existing approach on the on the flux, so similar to how there is a concatMap that calls the publish on vesPublisher, similar to how the map method in this App class works, if you make the kpiComputation method return a list and then wrap it in this class with a static method that puts it into a flux then the stream can operate on it, rather than having the kpiComputation unit try to handle both computation and publishing.",
